Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你復仇的機會 綺絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真矢的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去報仇吧 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道再生要花多少時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還有最後一手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人想起找爸爸媽媽的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找死人有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能替那些人活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命的記憶會創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽 還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣登？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒能寫下的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要由你來寫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我討厭這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別丟下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暉…和廣登一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 一個親人也保護不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是他留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的責任…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零央
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香 你是美三香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 我喘不過氣了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三Alvis原來的內核嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為爸爸的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘和人類軍肯定都會被那個內核控制著攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒必要承擔這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…你並沒有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿育的內核正在死亡邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你懷著和平的心願選擇了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好你沒事…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼困難的任務 你完成得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢和Mk.Nicht你都保護了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會違背內核的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來了啊 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你選擇的道路 我也會選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣登呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們把一部分遺體帶回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵人幹的 還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暉那邊我來解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經…不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來！遠見…前 輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人…這不是真的…阿廣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回家 廣登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定很疼吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後 你可以好好休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼！為什麼！為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同化現象是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸沒有感覺了 不管是熱 是冷 還是痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮有沒有問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道什麼時候會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓你消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們大家要一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天葬禮過後就辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辦什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成人禮啊 我們的成人禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對沃爾特先生說 讓他到島上來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我就想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道廣登平安的消息之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就寫個別的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望全世界的人都能知道龍宮島的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這條命要到頭了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你會遇見這架機體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就將成為你的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫皆城總士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你聽到這段話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該已經不在這個世界上了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才交給各位的Alvis訪問權限就是各位所肩負的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望各位尊重過去與你們同在之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相保護當下與你們同在之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,度過這個苦難的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位正是我們引以為傲的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnMingLiU\fs36\blur3\bord1\1a&H24&\c&HFFFFFF&}— 三天後 —
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海神島的兩個防護罩都已經修復
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒有偽裝鏡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過迎擊系統狀態良好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅶ和Mk.Ⅳ的改裝也已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(690,655)}conversion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可以出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍的動向怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大艦隊北上 沒有回應我們的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍擁有流浪者與第三部救世主型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是十分嚴重的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牽牛的情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據通識者的預測
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將在24小時內接近地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 上空的敵人正在阻礙阿育的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的要害就是流浪者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜部隊負責對付這個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大氣層外的敵人要怎麼對付？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西尾里奈和鏑木彗駕駛零式法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運用他們兩人的SDP將敵人拖到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何SDP在零式上都可以發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個方案在模擬中也是成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍由我們來對付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有需要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來和人類軍作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們學會的只有人類的可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人有時會變得十分可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我們仍然應該相信人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城總士 真壁一騎 遠見真矢 近藤劍司 近藤咲良 春日井甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立上芹 西尾里奈 鏑木彗 御門零央 水鏡美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會命令你們攻擊人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為法芙娜駕駛員 完成你們的使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡會成為未來的岔道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你告訴我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了 織姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的可以坐在暉前輩的位置上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會放大你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要把天上的敵人拖到我面前來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好跟他們說吧 為了不要後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貢 溝口先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明你們都是為阿廣而去了那麼危險的地方 我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒能完成任務 你怪我們是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會讓廣登的戰鬥白費的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都要平安回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的島就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全艦進入攻擊態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為應對與Festum的戰鬥 禁止與己方艦隊以外的對象通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四次蒼穹作戰現在開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上空出現敵群
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎擊系統全部啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海面上出現阿撒謝爾型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外部防護罩無法維持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維持航向 法芙娜部隊出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 按訓練時做的那樣匹配波長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 別老看我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了之後我會讓你看個夠的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精力執行計劃 明白沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的所羅門傳來消息 是阿撒謝爾型爬行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(970,655)}Crawler
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執行流浪者殲滅方案！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一至第三部隊 全機更新位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零式 啟動SDP！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們休想過去 Festum！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一隻！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩隻！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三隻！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕程式 啟動！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了沒那種程式啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往前衝 我來破壞敵人的力場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一起戰鬥真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真夠大的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也就這點能耐麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回歸——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虛無去——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到你們該待的虛無裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的力場已經瓦解！開始迎擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺到你的存在了 Festum！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的同化…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛我來承擔…你集中精神！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦隊 距離30單位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有艦隻均無法通信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度0 熄滅引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熄滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度降為0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在熄滅引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信頻道開放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不認為對方會回應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會把話送到！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D島停下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算拿自己當擋箭牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜大隊去鎮壓第三Alvis！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給他來個兩面夾擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狙擊 我們被攻擊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼遠的距離居然能打中？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人都沒死？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是沒打算殺我們…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告系統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誘導敵人 把他們當掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你的心臟嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下希望就會成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——以我們的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說再見了 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 敵人的力場又恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不攻擊D島嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還有利用價值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是太天真了呢 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救濟之火 任何時候看來都這麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我下來——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流浪者居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上的Mir掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算能打他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是在玩 來主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你讓我們戰鬥的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受你殺了那麼多人的報應吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 我也能開爸爸造的救世主型！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣 光弘！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別猶豫 一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是被灌輸了自己是人這個觀念的——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擋路——!!
